275
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:04,960
Here you are.

276
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,719
Take the medicine.

277
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:09,320
Master asked you to take care of me?

278
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:17,719
Ting Xue,

279
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,640
