Don't you know?

302
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:28,440
Because when my master

303
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,919
went through the Mortal World
with Supervisor Sage,

304
00:17:30,119 --> 00:17:31,759
you were not even born.

305
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,279
