313
00:17:51,999 --> 00:17:53,639
then she pushed me,

314
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:56,039
and even spilled the medicine you made.

315
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:58,759
- Nonsense, you spilled this medicine...
- Chong Zi,

316
