338
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,480
to send me up.

339
00:19:11,039 --> 00:19:12,680
How could this happen?

340
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,759
Even my master and you couldn't resist

341
00:19:14,759 --> 00:19:16,240
