374
00:21:29,039 --> 00:21:29,919
Master!

375
00:21:31,320 --> 00:21:32,320
Master!

376
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,200
Chong,

377
00:21:36,279 --> 00:21:37,600
go.

