00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:04,320
The barrier has been repaired
and the passage sealed.

401
00:24:04,799 --> 00:24:06,080
It will be firm forever.

402
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,279
Sage Chonghua has done
another great deed.

403
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:10,080
