admit her guilt under torture.

483
00:28:43,639 --> 00:28:44,519
Say it!

484
00:28:44,799 --> 00:28:46,200
How did you come back to life?

485
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,879
How did you find Sage Chonghua?

486
00:28:47,919 --> 00:28:50,200
